window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I was ready to say \"I do\", then my fiancé left me at the altar.</p> <p>Broken and embarrassed, Trace and Elliot helped me run away—ditching my wedding dress in the process.</p> <p>When I come back to the Wilder Retreat to show the world I’m no longer hurting, I know I must ignore my traitorous needs when it comes to these two men.</p> <p>Because my body wants them both.</p> <p>And my soul craves them just as much.</p> <p>I know I can’t choose, and part of me asks why I should.</p> <p>Only when we decide to take that chance and share everything, the danger from our pasts refuses to let our choice stand.</p> <p>With one kiss, one dance into temptation, we could lose everything.</p> <p>Including our lives.</p>"; 
